    <td valign="top">
      <h1>Infomous Help</h1>
      <p>This application is based on the <strong><a
      href="http://www.infomous.com" target="_blank">Infomous</a></strong>
      interactive text cloud technolgy.</p>
      
      <p>Word size indicates relevance; the larger the word, the more relevant
      it is to stories posted on the site throughout the day. Only the 40 or
      so most relevant words appear. Related terms and concepts are linked
      together with lines.</p>
      
      <p>Click a word to show links to relevant stories on the site. Click
      any link to open that link in a new page. Click anywhere to close the
      list. Double-click on a word to focus content around it. Focus mode
      places that word in the center of the screen and rearranges the rest
      of the cloud so that only those words related to the focus word remain
      in view. To exit focus and return to overview mode, click the pushpin
      icon. </p>
      
      <p>Find out more at <a href="http://www.infomous.com">the Infomous web
      site</a></p>
    </td>
